  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aims of this parallel two-arm pilot randomized controlled trial is to assess the
      feasibility and acceptability of an audio-recorded mindfulness-based intervention and to
      assess whether the intervention results in a clinically meaningful difference in physical
      activity compared to the control condition
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
